<div class="page-content">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="page-header">
      <h1 class="page-title">Refund and Exchange Policy</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="page-body">
      <div class="content-section">
        <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> {{ 'now' | date: '%B %d, %Y' }}</p>
        
        <h2>Return Period</h2>
        <p>We accept returns and exchanges within <strong>7 days</strong> of delivery. After this period, unfortunately, we cannot offer you a refund or exchange.</p>
        
        <h2>Eligibility for Returns</h2>
        <p>To be eligible for a return, your item must be:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>In the same condition that you received it</li>
          <li>Unworn or unused</li>
          <li>With tags and original packaging</li>
          <li>Accompanied by the receipt or proof of purchase</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Non-Returnable Items</h2>
        <p>Certain types of items cannot be returned:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Undergarments and intimate wear</li>
          <li>Items marked as "Final Sale" or "Non-Returnable"</li>
          <li>Customized or personalized items</li>
          <li>Items damaged by misuse or normal wear</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Return Process</h2>
        <p>To initiate a return:</p>
        <ol>
          <li>Contact our customer service team at <a href="tel:+919090949292">+91 9090949292</a> or <a href="mailto:ajay252551@gmail.com">ajay252551@gmail.com</a></li>
          <li>Provide your order number and reason for return</li>
          <li>Our team will guide you through the return process</li>
          <li>Pack the item(s) securely in original packaging</li>
          <li>Ship or bring the item(s) to our store</li>
        </ol>
        
        <h2>Exchange Policy</h2>
        <p>We offer exchanges for:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Different sizes (subject to availability)</li>
          <li>Different colors (subject to availability)</li>
          <li>Defective items</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Refund Processing</h2>
        <p>Once we receive and inspect your return:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>If approved, refunds will be processed within 5-7 business days</li>
          <li>Refunds will be issued to the original payment method</li>
          <li>You will receive an email confirmation once the refund is processed</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Shipping Costs</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Return shipping costs are the responsibility of the customer unless the item was defective or incorrect</li>
          <li>Original shipping costs are non-refundable</li>
          <li>We recommend using a trackable shipping service for returns</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Damaged or Defective Items</h2>
        <p>If you receive a damaged or defective item:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Contact us immediately upon receipt</li>
          <li>Provide photos of the damage/defect</li>
          <li>We will arrange for replacement or full refund</li>
          <li>Return shipping will be covered by us</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Store Credit</h2>
        <p>In some cases, we may offer store credit instead of a refund. Store credit:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Never expires</li>
          <li>Can be used for any future purchases</li>
          <li>Is transferable to family members</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>For any questions about returns or exchanges:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Customer Care: <a href="tel:+919090949292">+91 9090949292</a></li>
          <li>Sales Enquiries: <a href="tel:+919090949393">+91 9090949393</a> | <a href="tel:+919910134560">+91 9910134560</a></li>
          <li>Email: <a href="mailto:ajay252551@gmail.com">ajay252551@gmail.com</a></li>
          <li>Visit our store: RZ-2/275, Shankar Park, Sagar Pur West, Opp Baba Balak Nath Temple, New Delhi - 110046</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

